reviewText: I got about halfway through when the tutorial stopped matching up with the workspace. Whatever the issue was made it impossible to move forward in the project without an error message. I reported the problem but still havent received any help, though I'd love to finish the course.

I​'m not the least inclined to complete this course, solely because the format is near impossible to work with on a 14 inch screen. Split screen on a small screen has made it rather difficult for me to work efficiently, and making errors while going through the course has resulted in me having to start over a couple of times. Not worth it. A Follow Along link via YouTube would have made more sense.

Great guided project content wise, with data sets and, series of short videos, practice assignments. I had no prior experience or knowledge of Power BI, still I was able to follow the hands-on steps.  Maybe some knowledge of Excel helped through it. I didn't give 5 stars because of the practice assignments: here I couldn't see how to do the assignment from the virtual desktop (what the instructor was asking). But it was no big deal as  I see the assignments as an extra bonus; beside, I can still exercise with these practice assignments afterward in my own time. Hence, a very good project! I enjoyed doing it. Thank you!
